{"tid":1442964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（重要）提提大家 小心比鬼捉實","createTime":"2019-08-11T05:56:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:11:46.000Z","uid":53039,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0dec735a2b21db560efd5e564af0f0ac20073fb7","tid":1442964,"uid":53039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"如果今日唔夠人 大家一定要小心班狗沖過黎果陣會比鬼捉實你唔比你走 而且你唔會知班手足有面有幾多鬼（估計唔會小）所以大家要趁人小既時候留意下手足入面有冇咩人行跡可疑"},{"pid":"97bd059506f3a8013bc2c4f650aeb563f0dc0658","tid":1442964,"uid":73826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:00:36.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"07bf2790603a782a205e3a28a6242f00e56eea21","tid":1442964,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:01:26.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"0e107e4802a6d7dffdc24b4e97adba3dee888a75","tid":1442964,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6a403b31771ec2aa92bac56c8856ba5975a444b","tid":1442964,"uid":53039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:22:31.000Z","msg":"推比大家睇到"},{"pid":"476bdc0c9944f08f297e5d8ac26cb72ad78d2832","tid":1442964,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:28:57.000Z","msg":"邊個捉人即<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd1eb672b569240431d568657a4fdea2ba3aa4d","tid":1442964,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:29:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">針對警方無差別襲擊，標籤為<span style=\"color: red;\">國家恐怖主義武裝組織</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣核彈 - 為恐怖主義正名</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEh1L51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEh1L51.jpg&h=6b5d83e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖主義標籤係諸國用嚟打壓異己嘅手法，「國家當局可用以將政敵或其他對手非法化，從而使國家武裝部隊可理直氣壯地打擊敵人」，包括支那對新疆嘅打壓，都係以打擊恐怖主義為名，效果顯著。若果我地為警隊嘅恐怖主義正名，絕對係致命打擊警隊嘅合法性同認受性嘅方法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢標籤我地做港獨，我地標籤返佢做「國家恐怖主義份子」 正名標籤警方為非法嘅武裝組織</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1426058\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1426058</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別襲擊製造恐怖氣氛絕對已經係恐怖主義！我地係嘅係要為警隊嘅行為正名！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">警隊失控無差別襲擊，係屬於國家恐怖主義嘅行為，已經超越「過度暴力」、「濫捕」同「濫用暴力」，依啲字眼淡化佢嘅「拐帶」、「恐怖襲擊」等非法行為，警隊嘅行為喺好多國家已經係可以定義為失去合法性啲武裝組織。<br />\n而且加上721恐襲同打後嘅黑警合作，有理由相信依個恐怖主義組織係跨越明同暗。現時警察喺民間嘅認受性極低，成為過街老鼠，執法行動已變質，失去合法地執行職務嘅能力，街坊見到警察嘅武裝會產生恐懼感。恐怖主義管治已引起社會及國際極度不安。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fool1-1.fna&amp;oh=58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026&amp;oe=5DD55B02\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fool1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F67630995_110432746967840_2331413204384612352_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQl4L1bx4RYkXXmGjLvLvV0mieI9WjtsALdVP9McHQyfw-djgsY6ZSsf-1vl88RayEY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fool1-1.fna%26oh%3D58b06b4db0bdb4fb6b665e75af38d026%26oe%3D5DD55B02&h=2d15fa1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無差別化武襲擊！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">[過期催淚彈][有圖] 毒到連眼都起水泡！！！！！麻煩全世界前線中線後線街坊啊婆啊伯！！戴靚少少既Gear唔該！！！！！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436725</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認同請聯署請分享</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fofficially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization&d=haqyWHVU0l66G8glzozbUzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=bb801a19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/officially-recognize-hong-kong-police-force-hkpf-led-commissioner-stephen-lo-wai-chung-terrorist-organization</a><br />\n已有<span style=\"color: orange;\">47,835</span>/100,000個簽名（11 Aug 2019 at 14:29）<br />\n［白宮聯署］香港警察為恐怖組織<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427701\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427701</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑合作 恐怖治國<br />\n警察本色 恐怖組織</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">槍炮化武 無差別襲擊<br />\n警黑勾結 武裝巴結<br />\nHKPF IS STATE TERRORIST!<br />\nNO STATE TERRORISM!<br />\nNO INDISCRIMINATE ATTACK!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n821守衛香港 反警黑恐怖治國 反恐大遊行/集會（未定）<br />\n821 - 元朗恐襲紀念日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442294</a>"},{"pid":"53f2dc44ba48419bf9a846e6ac8d2ae613bfd90a","tid":1442964,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:29:30.000Z","msg":"團結就是力量<br />\n追究警黑勾結"},{"pid":"849d650d82bdf730658c256299273992ccf6e735","tid":1442964,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a13db2859b44440c9c0111846a0a8ea70796977c","tid":1442964,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:30:21.000Z","msg":"有戒備心就夠<br />\n唔洗太疑心玩捉鬼"},{"pid":"85f553b69ca5bf81f38ba13367e2d1a29bc30c3d","tid":1442964,"uid":262263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有人捉住你<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔俾你走</span></span>就一拳打過去</span>"},{"pid":"3ba535a86f04396aaf286b2760f5404a2952c6b4","tid":1442964,"uid":287096,"like":0,"d